<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Johannes Weinheim</head><p>Der Rat dankt für die Unterstützung des Hans Maurer, Diener der Stadt, bei Pfalzgraf Ludwig III. bei Rhein, und kündigt Maurer erneut an.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_62" id="30r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_62_r1l18">Johannes vveynheim </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_62_r1l19">Erſamer vnd lıeber <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> VVeynheim . Vns hat hanns <expan>Mawr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> dıener </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_62_r1l20">den wır nehſt ʒu <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> gnedıgen <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ~ dem <expan>Pfallncʒgraf<ex>en</ex></expan> von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_62_r1l21"><expan>gnedıg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>cʒog</expan> <expan>ſtepf<ex>an</ex></expan> ſeıns <expan>brud<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> geſant <expan>hette<ex>n</ex></expan> wol ge - </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_62_r1l22">ſagt vvıe Jr eẅch in <expan>denſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> ſachen gar freẅntlıch vnd wıllıg </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_62_r1l23">beweıſet habt / des wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>fleıſſıkl<ex>ich</ex></expan> danken vnd vmb eẅch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_62_r1l24"><expan>beg<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>ʒuu<ex>er</ex>ſchulden</expan> / Alſo <expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> wır <expan>denſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_62_r1l25">ʒu dem <expan>vorgen<ex>anten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>gnedıg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ~ dem <expan>Pfallncʒgraf<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd auch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_62_r1l26">mıt eẅch <expan>dauo<ex>n</ex></expan> ʒu reden / Vnd <expan>bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅr <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> mıt fleıſſ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_62_r1l27">in bona <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan> credencıe ut <expan>ſup<ex>ra</ex></expan> <expan>mutat<ex>is</ex></expan> <expan>muta<ex>n</ex>dıs</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_62_r1l28"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſup<ex>ra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_62" id="30r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Johannes Weynheim </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Ersamer und lieber <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> Weynheim,
                                                uns hat Hanns <expan>Mawr<ex>er</ex></expan>,
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> diener, den wir
                                                nehst zu <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> gnedigen
                                                  <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, dem
                                                  <expan>pfallnczgraf<ex>en</ex></expan>, von
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>czog</expan>
<expan>Stepf<ex>an</ex></expan>, seins
                                                  <expan>brud<ex>er</ex>s</expan>,
                                                  <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> gesant
                                                  <expan>hette<ex>n</ex></expan> wol gesagt, wie ir
                                                ewch in <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan> sachen gar
                                                frewntlich und willig beweiset habt, des wir
                                                  <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>fleissikl<ex>ich</ex></expan> danken und umb
                                                ewch <expan>beg<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>zu v<ex>er</ex>schulden</expan>. Also
                                                  <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan> wir
                                                  <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> zu dem
                                                  <expan>vorgen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> dem
                                                  <expan>pfallnczgraf<ex>en</ex></expan> und auch
                                                mit ewch <expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan> zu reden und
                                                  <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> ewr
                                                  <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> mit fleiss in
                                                bona <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan> credencie ut
                                                  <expan>sup<ex>ra</ex></expan>
<expan>mutat<ex>is</ex></expan>
<expan>muta<ex>n</ex>dis</expan>.
                                                  <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                                                  <expan>sup<ex>ra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
